  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The inmate who tried to move the charger was caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Police Special Task Force says that an inmate who tried to take two mobile phones, two batteries and two battery chargers (chargers) into the Welikada remand prison was arrested.",
        "Police say that the officers of the Welikada Prison Police Special Task Force camp found these chargers and batteries hidden in the trouser pockets while checking the inmates.",
        "Police Sergeant 6083 Wickramasinghe of the Welikada prison camp arrested the suspects on the instructions of the Special Task Force Commander DIG Attorney General Varuna Jayasundara."
      ],
